# W04｜Linux 系統基礎：檔案系統、權限、程序與服務管理

## FHS 路徑表

| FHS 路徑 | FHS 定義 | Docker 用途 |
|---|---|---|
| /etc/docker/ | Stores configuration files for Docker | configure Docker daemon settings|
| /var/lib/docker/ | Stores persistent application data | Stores Docker images, containers, volumes, and metadata |
| /usr/bin/docker | Stores executable programs | Docker CLI command used to interact with Docker |
| /run/docker.sock | Stores runtime process | communication between Docker CLI and Docker daemon |

