## 權限結構

### Docker Socket 權限解讀
（貼上 `ls -la /var/run/docker.sock` 輸出，逐欄說明 owner/group/others 的權限）
srw-rw---- 1 root docker 0 Apr 23 09:45 /var/run/docker.sock

- s: indicates this is a socket file used for communication between Docker CLI and Docker daemon
- rw- (owner): the owner (root) has read and write permission
- rw- (group): the group (docker) has read and write permission
- --- (others): other users have no permission
- owner: root
- group: docker

